                                                <h4>next story</h4>
                                                <a class="permalink" href="/fashion/blogs/dressed/2015/02/grammys-best-dressed-2015" title="Nicki Minaj, Rihanna, Taylor Swift: Vote for the Grammy Awards Best Dressed Now!"><img src="/images/fashion/2015/02/best-dressed-grammys-dresses-2015-w724.jpg">Nicki Minaj, Rihanna, Taylor Swift: Vote for the Grammy Awards Best Dressed Now!</a>
